*Namerno* je naslikao to da bi privukao pažnju. (He deliberately painted it to draw attention.)

Nije to bilo *namerno*. (It wasn't done deliberately.)

Ona je *namerno* pokazala da je slobodna. (She deliberately showed that she was free.)

On je *namerno* zanemario njene reči. (He deliberately ignored her words.)

On je *namerno* pravio probleme. (He was deliberately causing trouble.)